==Slovak==
===Etymology===
:From Latin stem '''firm''' in ''confirmatio'', changed into '''birm''' = '''-ovanie''' (''-ation'')
===Noun===
:'''birmovanie''' ''n'', '''birmovania''' ''pl''
:'''birmovan''' ''stem''
:{{decpat}} {{vysvedcenie}}
# (''religion'') [[confirmation]]
#:'''sviatosť birmovania''' &ndash; ''sacrament of confirmation''

:''Note:'' The word ''birmovanie'' is common among Slovak Catholics. Slovak Lutherans use the word ''[[konfirmácia]]''.

